    <item>
      <title>这是特勤局罕见的致命枪击事件</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/secret-service-fatal-shootings.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，一名武装男子在特朗普总统的佛罗里达俱乐部被枪杀，这是该机构 160 年历史上为数不多的致命事件之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/secret-service-fatal-shootings.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 23:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特勤局称武装男子在海湖庄园被枪杀</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/mar-a-lago-shooting-secret-service.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地治安官确认这名男子是北卡罗来纳州卡梅伦市的一名 21 岁居民。总统当时并不在佛罗里达州的度假胜地，也没有对枪击事件发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/mar-a-lago-shooting-secret-service.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 23:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当面对种族主义指控时，特朗普将矛头指向了他的黑人朋友</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-black-people-history.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当特朗普总统被要求讨论与黑人选民有关的任何事情时，他经常援引他未透露姓名的黑人朋友，或被点名的名人和运动员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-black-people-history.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 23:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
