      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/weather/storm-nyc-preparations-mamdani.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一月下旬的风暴已经够糟糕的了。这次带来了真正的暴风雪情况，该市已加强了应对措施。]]></description>
