    <item>
      <title>尽管国家镇压，伊朗学生连续第二天抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/world/middleeast/iran-student-protests.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[学生团体报告称，伊朗两个最大城市的大学发生了抗议活动，因为政府正在努力应对国内的不满情绪和美国罢工的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/world/middleeast/iran-student-protests.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 22:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑对伊朗进行有针对性的打击，随后进行更大规模的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-iran-strike-attack.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高级谈判代表计划周四在日内瓦举行最后一搏会谈，讨论一项新提案，该提案可能会在两个航母战斗群集结在伊朗打击范围内时创建一个出口匝道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-iran-strike-attack.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 21:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
